data.description: Welcome Home! This spacious 2 bedroom, 2 bath home has been updated and is ready for you to move right in. Open floor plan with plenty of natural light and modern finishes. Upgrades include new interior paint, new bath and kitchen tile flooring, new custom bath vanity, and so much more! The open kitchen features shaker style cabinetry, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The family room flows effortlessly from the dining room. Enjoy the Florida sunshine with family and friends on the screened patio, and oversized privacy fenced backyard. New AC 2021. Water Heater 2018. No HOA. Home is perfectly located for easy access to US HWY 19, Suncoast Parkway, Tampa International Airport, amusement parks, nearby restaurants, and Beaches. Home will not last long! Book your private showing today.
